%B0-giai-t%C3%A1c-h%E1%BB%B7-ph%E1%BB%A5c/poem-UyhRR53jTD1dNcb5KwP2-Q">Quý Hợi lạp nhị thập ngũ dạ đắc Thiếu Nguyên đáp hoạ chư giai tác hỷ phục - 癸亥腊二十五夜得少原答和諸佳作喜復</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-N%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Thu-t%E1%BB%A9/poem-TRf3kTzhB20rgbGH5q4-yg">Thu tứ - 秋思</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-N%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-PSgXCHLe22-Whw_BN8uK9A">Trương Ngọc Nương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/U-gi%E1%BA%A3n-tuy%E1%BB%81n/poem-EWXqNfXDGvE8oGnx69xyyQ">U giản tuyền - 幽澗泉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%97/V%C5%A9-l%C3%A2m-linh/poem-PwoDHYt9NtuoX-5A-mbj2Q">Vũ lâm linh - 雨霖鈴</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%97/author-uSefdg6gWPnl7XHeM-UXCw">Trương Hỗ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
